title: Justin Time for Week Three
description:
Mina and SB Nation's Justis Mosqueda preview Bucs-Rams and discuss wide ranging NFL topics like- should we be worried about the rookie quarterbacks? Will the Packers' defense be their undoing? Are the Raiders legit? Are you buying on Teddy Bridgewater? And how good is the Panthers' defense?
